data.title: The Observer - New Review - 1806
data.meta_description: The Observer - New Review_1806 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document is an agenda for a publication that includes summaries of upcoming articles and interviews, as well as listings of critics' reviews, books, puzzles, and television programs. The cover story features an interview with acclaimed actor Mark Rylance, in which he responds to questions from readers. Other articles include a profile of artist Ryan Gander, photographs by Nicholas Blair from 1980s America, and an examination of whether the US government is covering up UFO sightings and alien spacecraft landings.
